    "For example, the volitional act of approaching the door causes it to \"swing open. \"",
    "Similarly, autonomic responses to the feeling that \"something is wrong\" produces goosebumps that provides further evidence that \"something is wrong. \"",
    "In light of this discussion, how this may manifest over longer periods is relevant.",
    "The Bayesian Brain, FEP and AI have all been discussed within the area of niche construction (Constant et al., 2018), where organisms experience long-term influence over their immediate environment (their niche) and are able to enter into what could be considered \"low surprise, \" longitudinal relationships with their sensory inputs around them.",
